I have 80 mage. 200M to spend. But i don't want to lose money while doing this, i need a way in which i could make money at least, idc if i make 1gp everytime i do it. i just don't want to lose. but i'll lose 1gp everytime if it comes to that..The least Possible to lose, the Max possible to make...Any suggestions?
Im guessing High alching is my best bet here...? any suggestions on how i should go about it?
Take note, the account that has 80 mage is perm muted, and main is locked and f2p.
